{"html":"<style>\n* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n.slide {\n  width: 1080px;\n  height: 1350px;\n  background: #0D0D0D;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\n}\n.glow-top {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 700px;\n  height: 700px;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(244,192,0,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);\n  top: -200px;\n  right: -150px;\n}\n.glow-bottom {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 500px;\n  height: 500px;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(46,31,163,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);\n  bottom: -150px;\n  left: -100px;\n}\n.grid-lines {\n  position: absolute;\n  inset: 0;\n  background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);\n  background-size: 80px 80px;\n}\n.content {\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 3;\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: 0 80px;\n}\n.badge {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 12px;\n  border: 2px solid rgba(244,192,0,0.5);\n  color: #F4C000;\n  font-size: 18px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  letter-spacing: 4px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  padding: 10px 28px;\n  margin-bottom: 64px;\n}\n.badge-dot {\n  width: 10px;\n  height: 10px;\n  background: #F4C000;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 14px #F4C000;\n}\n.headline {\n  font-family: Anton, sans-serif;\n  font-size: 96px;\n  color: #FFFFFF;\n  line-height: 1.0;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n.headline .yellow {\n  color: #F4C000;\n  display: block;\n}\n.divider {\n  width: 60px;\n  height: 4px;\n  background: #F4C000;\n  margin: 0 auto 48px;\n}\n.sub {\n  font-size: 26px;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);\n  font-weight: 300;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  margin-bottom: 80px;\n  max-width: 720px;\n}\n.swipe-hint {\n  font-size: 17px;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\n  letter-spacing: 3px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n}\n.logo {\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: 56px;\n  right: 72px;\n  width: 72px;\n  opacity: 0.6;\n  z-index: 4;\n}\n.step-indicator {\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: 60px;\n  left: 80px;\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 8px;\n  z-index: 4;\n}\n.dot {\n  width: 28px;\n  height: 4px;\n  background: #F4C000;\n  border-radius: 2px;\n}\n.dot-inactive {\n  width: 12px;\n  height: 4px;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\n  border-radius: 2px;\n}\n</style>\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"glow-top\"></div>\n  <div class=\"glow-bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"grid-lines\"></div>\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <div class=\"badge\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Advertencia &middot; PC Clean</div>\n    <div class=\"headline\">\n      5 hábitos<br>que están<br>matando<br><span class=\"yellow\">tu PC.</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n    <div class=\"sub\">Y ni siquiera<br>te das cuenta.<br>Desliza antes del próximo error.</div>\n    <div class=\"swipe-hint\">Desliza para descubrirlos &rarr;</div>\n  </div>\n  <img class=\"logo\" src=\"/uploads/64d70ecd-3300-4ef3-b614-7839245e41fb.png\" />\n  <div class=\"step-indicator\">\n    <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n    <div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>","notes":"Slide 1 (parte 2): Portada cinematográfica oscura con glow, grid y badge — 5 hábitos que están matando tu PC."}